`success`, `warning`, or `critical` alongside descriptive text."},"857":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart-18","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart#label-type","content":"Control the font size of the primary label using `labelType`. Use `'value'` for numeric or percentage values and `'text'` for short descriptive strings."},"858":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart-19","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart#gauge-not-sizing-correctly","content":"The component uses `container-type: inline-size` and fills its parent width. Ensure the parent has a defined width:"},"859":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart-20","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart#value-out-of-range","content":"Values outside the valid range are clamped silently at runtime. For continuous mode the range is 0–100; for segmented mode the range is 0 to the segment count."},"860":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"page","content":"DonutChart","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components","Chart"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart"},"861":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-0","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","content":"Donut charts are for parts-to-whole comparison—how partial elements add up to a total—shown as a ring so a few categories are easy to compare at a glance."},"862":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-1","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#installation","content":"Installation"},"863":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-2","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#props","content":"Props"},"864":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-3","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#examples","content":"Examples"},"865":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-4","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#basic","content":"Basic"},"866":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-5","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#single-slice","content":"Single slice"},"867":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-6","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#legend-placement","content":"Legend placement"},"868":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-7","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#small-slices","content":"Small slices"},"869":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-8","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#format-value","content":"Format value"},"870":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-9","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#basic","content":"You give the chart a `data` array (`id`, `name`, `value`) and a `label` in the middle—this is the everyday setup when you want several categories on one ring and a headline number or title in the hole."},"871":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart-10","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/donut-chart#single-slice","content":"When there is only one slice, the ring is full. Add `subLabel` if you want a smaller second line under the main center text."},"872":{"id":"/do