vious checkbox"],[830,"**Simplify tooltips**: If tooltips are complex, consider using simpler content or disabling them"],[705,"**Single and multi-series support**: Display one or multiple data series with grouped bars"],[832,"**Single Series**: Basic vertical bar chart"],[568,"**Space** (in multi-select): Toggle selection of focused item"],[474,"**Space**: Select the focused radio button"],[166,"**Space**: Toggles the focused checkbox"],[337,"**Space/Enter**: Opens menu and activates items"],[562,"**Space/Enter**: Opens the popover and focuses the selected item"],[526,"**Space/Enter**: Select the focused segment"],[289,"**Sprite Sheet Creation**: A hidden SVG sprite sheet is automatically injected into the DOM containing symbol definitions"],[299,"**SSR Limitation**: Sprite references render empty until client-side hydration"],[804,"**Sticky axes**: Positioned absolutely to remain visible during scroll"],[793,"**Sticky y-axis**: The y-axis remains visible during horizontal scroll"],[239,"**Styling**: `className`, `style`, `data-*` attributes"],[283,"**SVG Parsing**: The fetched SVG string is parsed into a React element using `@bento/svg-parser`"],[343,"**Tab**: Closes menu and moves to next element"],[566,"**Tab**: Moves focus to the next focusable element"],[165,"**Tab**: Moves focus to the next/previous checkbox"],[471,"**Tab**: Moves focus to/from the radio group"],[524,"**Tab**: Moves focus to/from the segmented controller"],[95,"**Text** (optional) — Description block rendered when `description` is provided."],[808,"**Tooltips** use absolute positioning and scroll-aware calculations for accurate placement"],[797,"**Tooltips**: Show on both hover and focus for keyboard users"],[298,"**Trade-offs:**"],[240,"**Transform**: `rotate`, `flip` for icon transformations"],[557,"**Trigger Button:** `data-pressed`, `data-disabled`, `data-focused`, `aria-expanded`"],[567,"**Type to select**: Type characters to jump to matching options"],[344,"**Type to select**: Type to jump to matching items"],[754,"**Type**: `(value: string | number | Date) => string`"],[758,"**Type**: `(value: string | number | Date) => string`"],[772,"**Type**: `[number, number] | string[]`"],[760,"**Type**: `number`"],[762,"**Type**: `number`"],[767,"**Type**: `string[] | [number, number]`"],[736,"**Type**: `string`"],[738,"**Type**: `string`"],[1061,"**Typed Refs:** Refs are correctly typed based on the `as` value - `useRef<HTMLButtonElement>` works with `as=\"button\"`."],[233,"**TypeScript support**: Fully typed with comprehensive prop interfaces"],[714,"**TypeScript support**: Fully typed with comprehensive prop interfaces"],[301,"**Use default mode** for SSR applications or when icons appear infrequently"],[1120,"**Use Grid when**: You need explicit two-dimensional layouts with rows and columns, named grid areas, or responsive auto-fill patterns."],[302,"**Use sprite mode** when the same icons appear many times (navigation, lists, tables)"],[312,"**Use sprite mode**: For repeated icons, consider sprite mode which consolidates multiple icons into a single SVG sprite sheet, reducing DOM size and improving performance when the same icon appears multiple times"],[605,"**Validation states**: Use `isInvalid` with `errorMessage` and `isDisabled` for validation and disabled state"],[988,"**Value formatting**: You can supply a function to format each value; if you don't, the tooltip shows the point's `y` (or nothing when null). Use the formatter for custom data shapes."],[826,"**Verify event targets**: Tooltips use mouse event coordinates and bar group positions"],[706,"**Vertical and horizontal orientations**: Choose the best layout for your data and use case"],[802,"**Vertical charts**: Horizontal scrolling when many data points exceed container width"],[82,"**Visual frame**: Shared border, focus, disabled, and invalid styling around field content"],[715,"**VisX integration**: Leverages VisX primitives for scales, axes, shapes, and responsive layout"],[288,"**Wha